r Konzipierung von diskriminierungsfreien Institutionen im Bildungssektor bei. Das Buch bietet zudem einer breiten Leserschaft differenzierte Einblicke in ein spannendes gesellschaftliches Thema.  aDiversity - obtaining a university free from discrimination by making structural changes? Study about equal opportunity in the field of education.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aDiscrimination in education. 4aBildung. 4aChancengleichheit. 4aDiskriminierung. 4aGender Studies. 4aHochschule. 4aPädagogik. 4aRassismus. 4aSoziale Gerechtigkeit. 4aSoziale Ungleichheit. 4aUniversität. 7aEDUCATION / Organizations & Institutions.2bisacsh  aDiscrimination.  aEducation.  aEqual Opportunity.  aGender Studies.  aPedagogy.  aRacism.  aSocial Inequality.  aSocial Justice.  aUniversity.1 aDarowska, Lucyna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDarowska, Lucyna, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEhret, Rebekka, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGhaderi, Cinur, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHertlein, Andrea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHornstein, René_Rain, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKaufmann, Margrit E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeiprecht, Rudolf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRichter, Caroline, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSatilmis, Ayla, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchlenzka, Nathalie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStern, Alex, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aS